OL,3,CKiller driver's 'woefully inadequate'
OL,4,Csentence to be reviewed
OL,6,FSenior judges will review the 10-year
OL,7,Fsentence given to a driver who killed
OL,8,Ftwo teenagers in a crash after
OL,9,Fcomplaints it was "woefully
OL,10,Finadequate".
OL,12,FNatasha Allarakhia, 34, was driving at
OL,13,Fspeeds of almost 100mph on the A17
OL,14,Ftowards Sleaford, Lincolnshire,
OL,15,Fshortly before she ploughed into the
OL,16,Fback of a stationary Ford Festa.
