OL,3,CKiller driver's 'woefully inadequate'
OL,4,Csentence to be reviewed
OL,6,FWilliam Ray, 17, and 18 year-old Eddie
OL,7,FShore, who were waiting in the Fiesta
OL,8,Fat a red traffic light, both died. Two
OL,9,Fother passengers were taken to
OL,10,Fhospital.
OL,12,FLincoln Crown Court heard Allarakhia
OL,13,Fhad been taking sips of lager behind
OL,14,Fthe wheel and had her children in the
OL,15,Fcar with her when the crash happened
OL,16,Fin June 2024.
OL,18,FShe was serving a suspended sentence
OL,19,Fat the time of the crash and had
OL,20,Fprevious criminal convictions.
