OL,6,FAllarakhia was jailed for 10 years
OL,7,Flast month after admitting two counts
OL,8,Fof causing death by dangerous driving
OL,9,Fand one of causing serious injury by
OL,10,Fdangerous driving.
OL,12,FBut the Attorney General has now
OL,13,Fconfirmed the case has been referred
OL,14,Fto the Court of Appeal.
