OL,3,CKiller driver's 'woefully inadequate'
OL,4,Csentence to be reviewed
OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing, William's
OL,7,Fsisters told ITV News of their anger
OL,8,Fat the jail term.
OL,10,FHis family have launched a petition
OL,11,Fcalling for a review of sentences for
OL,12,Fdangerous drivers.
OL,14,FMs Johnson said: "I shared concerns
OL,15,Fwith the families and many other
OL,16,Fpeople that the sentence imposed... is
OL,17,Fwoefully inadequate."
OL,19,FShe added: "The Solicitor General has
OL,20,Fnow referred this case to the Court of
OL,21,FAppeal. I welcome this decision."
